cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >
  If you use SoftCap, SwishCap, or SparseCap in your work,
  please cite the paper below.
title: "Beyond ReLU and GELU: SoftCap Bounded Activations for Stability and Sparsity"
authors:
  - family-names: Cai
    given-names: Larry
    affiliation: "Monash Institute of Pharmaceutical Sciences, Monash University"
    email: "larry.cai@monash.edu"
  - family-names: Tang
    given-names: Jie
    affiliation: "Monash Institute of Pharmaceutical Sciences, Monash University"
