version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-03-01"
license: Apache-2.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/softcap-research/softcap"
abstract: >
  SoftCap introduces a family of three parametric activation functions
  (SoftCap, SwishCap, SparseCap) with bounded output range and controlled
  smoothness properties (C0, C1, C2 respectively). The family addresses
  representational collapse and anisotropic biases in deep learning,
  showing improved behaviour in grokking, out-of-distribution
  extrapolation, and sparse coding tasks relative to ReLU, GELU, and SiLU.
keywords:
  - activation functions
  - deep learning
  - isotropy
  - sparse representations
  - grokking
  - out-of-distribution generalization
